Which of the below procedures (A, B or C) is better for detecting salient edges in the image? Select one of them and explain why. Do not give text book explanation keep it simple and short as if written by a student.

 A) Compute the image gradients and then smooth these gradients using the Gaussian filter; 

B) Smooth the image pixel values and then compute the image gradients; 

C) Filter the image using the gradient of the Gaussian filter.
